---
title: Garlic-Cumin Grilled Chicken Sandos with Lime Mayo & Zesty Summer Salad
description: Bring your A-game to your Father’s Day cookout with these savory chicken sandwiches. Toasted brioche buns are spread with tangy lime mayo and filled with grilled garlic and cumin-rubbed chicken. Toss grilled sweet corn with charred zucchini, fresh tomato, and tangy lime for a colorful, summery side. No grill? No worries—a grill pan works just great!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66313c5c9eb2c19a07b967a9-4637d4cd.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/66313c5c9eb2c19a07b967a9-en-US.pdf
